    <statement id="536.txt-5">
      <text>blades linear to narrowly elliptic, 3–20 cm, margins usually pinnately lobed (with narrow rachis and linear lobes), rarely entire, apices acuminate, faces glabrous or lightly scurfy-puberulent.</text>
